  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dc0 \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dab\u0dba \u0d85\u0daf \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda\u0daf\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Election of the new president today in parliament",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The election of a member of parliament for the presidency vacated by the resignation of former president Gotabhaya Rajapaksa is scheduled to begin today (20th) at 10.00 am in parliament.",
        "Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe, leader of United National Party, Dallas Alahapperuma of Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna, Anura Kumara Dissanayake of National People's Force are joining the presidential battle.",
        "Since there is more than one candidate for the presidency, the new president will be elected by secret ballot.",
        "Also, each party has announced the candidate they are supporting. However, since there is a secret ballot, there is also an opportunity to vote outside the party decisions.",
        "The Speaker has asked all the MPs not to record who voted for whom."
      ],
